<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="sf-section reveal">
 <h2 class="professional-title section-title text-center reveal" class="section-title" class="professional-title" class="professional-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
 <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto">
  <div class="sf-faq-item">
   <div class="sf-faq-q">
    <span>What is a digital twin and how does it differ from a synthetic persona?</span>
    <span class="sf-faq-arrow">ş</span>
   </div>
   <div class="sf-faq-a">A digital twin is a virtual replica tied to a specific real individual for modeling and simulation. A synthetic persona is an AI-generated character not necessarily tied to a real person. Our governance applies to both with consent requirements.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="sf-faq-item">
   <div class="sf-faq-q">
    <span>How do we ensure consent for digital twin creation?</span>
    <span class="sf-faq-arrow">ş</span>
   </div>
   <div class="sf-faq-a">Our Digital Twin Governor verifies explicit informed consent before creation or use, with granular control over specific applications, time limits, and withdrawal mechanisms.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="sf-faq-item">
   <div class="sf-faq-q">
    <span>What happens to digital identities after death?</span>
    <span class="sf-faq-arrow">ş</span>
   </div>
   <div class="sf-faq-a">Our Legacy Management tools allow individuals to designate executors, configure posthumous access rules, and establish memorialization protocols respecting family wishes.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="sf-faq-item">
   <div class="sf-faq-q">
    <span>Can we detect unauthorized synthetic replicas?</span>
    <span class="sf-faq-arrow">ş</span>
   </div>
   <div class="sf-faq-a">Yes. Our Synthetic Persona Auditor uses behavioral biometrics, voice/face analysis, and pattern matching to identify unauthorized digital doubles with high confidence.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="sf-faq-item">
   <div class="sf-faq-q">
    <span>What compliance standards does this support?</span>
    <span class="sf-faq-arrow">ş</span>
   </div>
   <div class="sf-faq-a">We support GDPR, CCPA, healthcare privacy laws, and emerging digital identity regulations across 90+ countries with customizable compliance frameworks.</div>
  </div>
 </div>
</section>

